<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="cs">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title><%= title %></title>

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@400;500;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    :root {
      --bg-a: #050816;
      --bg-b: #0f172a;
      --panel: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.78);
      --panel-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      --text: #f8fafc;
      --muted: #94a3b8;
      --accent: #06b6d4;
      --accent-2: #7c3aed;
      --accent-3: #22c55e;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      min-height: 100vh;
      margin: 0;
      font-family: "Manrope", sans-serif;
      color: white;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 15% 10%, rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.2), transparent 28%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 85% 18%, rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.22), transparent 26%),
        linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-a), var(--bg-b));
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    body::before,
    body::after {
      content: "";
      position: fixed;
      border-radius: 999px;
      filter: blur(50px);
      opacity: 0.35;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    body::before {
      width: 260px;
      height: 260px;
      left: -70px;
      bottom: -80px;
      background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.18);
    }

    body::after {
      width: 220px;
      height: 220px;
      right: 40px;
      top: 120px;
      background: rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.14);
    }

    .page-shell {
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 34px 16px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .hero {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto 22px;
      padding: 18px 22px;
      border: 1px solid var(--panel-border);
      border-radius: 28px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
    }

    .hero-top {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 16px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    }

    .hero p {
      margin: 10px 0 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 58ch;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .hero-pill {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      color: #e2e8f0;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .hero-pill strong {
      color: #fff;
    }

    .results-grid {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .response-card {
      border: 1px solid var(--panel-border);
      border-radius: 24px;
      background: var(--panel);
      backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
      color: white;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.22);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .response-card-inner {
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .response-meta {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 14px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.92rem;
    }

    .response-meta strong {
      color: #fff;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .muted {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.92rem;
    }

    .response-body {
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 16px;
    }

    .field-row {
      padding: 14px 16px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);
    }

    .field-label {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #e2e8f0;
    }

    .field-dot {
      width: 10px;
      height: 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2));
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 5px rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.1);
    }

    .value-text {
      color: #f8fafc;
      line-height: 1.6;
      word-break: break-word;
    }

    .back-wrap {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 22px auto 0;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .btn-back {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-3), #16a34a);
      border: none;
      border-radius: 16px;
      font-weight: 700;
      padding: 0.9rem 1.25rem;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 30px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.18);
    }

    .btn-back:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      opacity: 0.97;
    }

    .badge-custom {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2));
      margin-right: 8px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 0.45em 0.72em;
    }

    @media (max-width: 576px) {
      .hero,
      .response-card-inner {
        padding: 16px;
      }

      .field-row {
        padding: 12px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <main class="page-shell">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-top">
        <div>
          <h1><%= title %></h1>
          <p>Přehled všech odpovědí v moderním panelu s kartami, aby bylo rychle vidět, co lidé volí nejčastěji.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-pill"><strong><%= responses.length %></strong> záznamů</div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <% if (responses.length === 0) { %>
      <div class="hero text-center">
        <p class="mb-0">Zatím nejsou žádné odpovědi.</p>
      </div>
    <% } %>

    <section class="results-grid">
      <% responses.forEach(r => { %>
        <article class="response-card">
          <div class="response-card-inner">
            <div class="response-meta">
              <div>
                <strong>ID <%= r.id %></strong>
                <div class="muted">Odesláno: <%= r.timestamp %></div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="response-body">
              <div class="field-row">
                <div class="field-label"><span class="field-dot"></span> Oblíbený den</div>
                <div class="value-text"><%= r.answers.den || r.answers.predmet %></div>
              </div>

              <div class="field-row">
                <div class="field-label"><span class="field-dot"></span> Pohyb</div>
                <div class="value-text"><%= r.answers.sport || r.answers.hodiny %></div>
              </div>

              <div class="field-row">
                <div class="field-label"><span class="field-dot"></span> Volný čas</div>
                <div class="value-text"><%= r.answers.volnycas || r.answers.uceni %></div>
              </div>

              <div class="field-row">
                <div class="field-label"><span class="field-dot"></span> Komentář</div>
                <div class="value-text"><%= r.answers.komentar || r.answers.zlepseni %></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      <% }) %>
    </section>

    <div class="back-wrap">
      <a href="/" class="btn btn-back px-4">
        Zpět na formulář
      </a>
    </div>

  </main>

</body>

</html>